# Design profile

Product purpose (what to build): `docs/PRODUCT.md` and `.cursor/rules/product.mdc`.

Quiet liquid glass on **mid dusk**. Low profile. Low texture. Minimal. Easy.

Shipping stack: Expo SDK 54, React Native, tokens + surfaces in `src/theme`.

## Atmosphere

- Single mode only — no light/dark toggle
- Canvas `#252B33`, deeper `#1B2026`, lift `#323942`
- Soft ink `#EEF1F4`, muted `#9199A4`, faint `#6E7682`
- Quiet steel accent `#B0C2CC` (muted fills via `accentSoft` / `accentMuted`)
- Screen backdrop: `MistBackdrop` (atmospheric fog washes) — not a flat void
- Forms sit **on** the mist — do not wrap auth / onboarding forms in glass cards

## Typography

- Display / hero: **Cormorant Garamond** (`fonts.display` / `displayItalic`)
- UI: **DM Sans** (`sans` / `sansMedium` / `sansSemi`)
- Onboarding / auth page titles: split lead + italic trail (`type.hero` + `type.heroItalic`), e.g. “Add” + “*photos*”
- Uppercase micro-labels use `type.label` + muted color
- Never default to Inter / system stacks for headlines

## Chrome & controls

- Tokens only from `src/theme` — never invent brand colors
- Glass via `GlassSurface` / `expo-blur` for **bars, sheets, modals, key listing surfaces** — hairline borders, soft wash, whisper shadow
- Fields: `colors.field` / `fieldFocus`, radius `control` / `lg`, hairline borders
- Primary CTA obvious; secondary / skip / back quieter (`Button` variants `primary` | `ghost` | `quiet`)
- Progress: thin hairline dots, accent when active — not pill clusters

## Icons

- Pack: **Lucide** (`lucide-react-native` + `react-native-svg`)
- Always render via `Icon` (`src/components/ui/Icon`) — sizes/`iconStroke` from `src/theme/icons`
- Quiet stroke (~1.75); active nav can nudge to 2. Prefer outline glyphs over filled
- Canonical nav glyphs: `Home`, center `Plus`, `Landmark` (Bank). Import named icons from Lucide; don’t mix icon libraries

## Product patterns (keep consistent)

- **Bottom nav** (`BottomNav`): floating glass dock — **Home** · large steel **circular +** · **Bank**. Compact organic blob sized to the controls (no sparse empty glass). Center hugs the + face; soft taper to the ends. Not edge-to-edge. Tabs use Lucide + uppercase micro-labels.
- **Main shell** (`MainShell`): Home / Bank tabs; boards and balances from the API
- **Home**: split hero (“Near” + “*you*”), open / active / history drive boards, clear space for floating dock
- **Driver listing** (`DriverCard`): profile surface — PFP avatar, `Name · VehicleType` same size on one line, phone, seats/years detail, optional exterior/interior thumbs
- **Photos step**: circular PFP for “You”; rectangular pickers for vehicle interior / exterior (max one each). Shared pick queue — don’t block sibling slots
- **Location step**: permission only — no driver-card preview on that screen. Expo Go maxes at While Using; Always needs a native build
- **You’re in**: driver card + “Need to make changes? Go to Settings.” — no map chrome there
- Dismiss keyboard on empty taps / continue / back during forms

## Do

- One purpose per screen; generous `space` tokens; clear hierarchy
- Soft press (`motion.pressScale` ~0.985), short ease (~160–240ms)
- Success / danger from tokens (`success`, `danger`) — quiet, not neon

## Don’t

- No logo / wordmark chrome in-app UI
- No “AI product” look: purple/indigo gradients, neon glow, pitch-black cosmic themes, pill clusters, emoji flourishes, multi-layer shadows
- No warm cream + terracotta + serif newspaper layouts
- No busy textures, gradients as decoration, inset media hero cards, floating badges on media
- Don’t card-wrap everything — reserve glass for intentional surfaces
- Don’t dual-theme

## Motion

Soft press, short ease. Presence, not noise.
